photos.alt: A photo of a person sitting on a bench in a park from afar. The person is wearing a bright orange hoodie with the hood on, and is looking at something on their phone. The photo is vertical, and high poplar trees can be visible on both sides of the bench, going high beyond the photo's frame. An out-of-focus grass with small white flowers is in the foreground, and some other trees and bushes are in the background.
